<p style="Heading 1"><c props="lang:en-GB"></c>1.0.0 Changelog</p>
<p style="Normal">These are just the changes between 0.99.5 and 1.0.0. They are not real release notes.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">David Chart</p>
<p style="Normal">Documentation bug fixes.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Jeremy Davis</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix for building with Visual C 7.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix Win32 build by renaming a page size variable that got missed.</p>
<p style="Normal">Win32 build fixes.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Andrew Dunbar</p>
<p style="Normal">Solaris iconv fixes.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Hubert Figuiere</p>
<p style="Normal">Build instructions update.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Frank Franklin</p>
<p style="Normal">Build system work.</p>
<p style="Normal">Renamed some variables to avoid namespace clashes, and then renamed the rest of the page size variables as well to make the code pretty.</p>
<p style="Normal">Made Gaelic visible.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixes for language IDs.</p>
<p style="Normal">Committed the new help files so that they are included with builds.</p>
<p style="Normal">Build fix so that CREDITS.TXT is made available to the documentation (which links to it).</p>
<p style="Normal">Added aboutos.info to help files.</p>
<p style="Normal">Support for debs in abispell.</p>
<p style="Normal">Change install permissions for ttfadmin.sh so that it isn't world-executable.</p>
<p style="Normal">Committed the final fix to the vexed question of what to call Catala(n). (No 'n').</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes, including 1531, 3099, 3137.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Stephane Fritsch</p>
<p style="Normal">BeOS build fix.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Luis Miguel Garcia</p>
<p style="Normal">Spanish localisation update.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Gabriel Gerhardsson</p>
<p style="Normal">Spelling rpm update.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added Esperanto to spellchecker.</p>
