<p style="Normal">Japanese localisation update.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Marco Innocenti</p>
<p style="Normal">Italian localisation update.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Dom Lachowicz</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix spellchecking on QNX and NetBSD.</p>
<p style="Normal">ABW exporter tweaks.</p>
<p style="Normal">Removed the old help files.</p>
<p style="Normal">Help file updates.</p>
<p style="Normal">Help search page.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix a clash in accelerator keys.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes, including 1028, 1742, 2645, 3148.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Pat Lam</p>
<p style="Normal">Technical ut_string improvements.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed bug with cursor placement around images.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes, including 857, 1066, 1965, 2433, 2511, 2918.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Per Larsson</p>
<p style="Normal">Swedish localisation update.</p>
